  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    MyHMCTS introduces Multi-Factor Authentication
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Introduction of multi-factor authentication, to provide additional security protection to account users.</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
